data.description: Incredible price adjustment!! Welcome home to this recently renovated ranch-style charmer in the award-winning Etowah School district. Experience a true sense of community in this friendly neighborhood with year-round activities for all! Enjoy morning coffee or an evening beverage on the covered front porch. Inside, this home offers the ease of one-level living in an open floor plan with high ceilings and large windows that flood the space with natural light. The chef's kitchen is a wonderful highlight, featuring granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a handy island that's ideal for food preparation and extra seating. With all of today's popular finishes, this kitchen is both stylish and functional. The main level primary suite includes a spectacular ensuite bathroom with a glass walk-in shower and a separate soaking tub. Two more cheery bedrooms and another completely updated bathroom on the main level ensure comfort and convenience for everyone. LVP flooring throughout not only adds beauty but also offers durability and easy care. Step out to the party-sized deck overlooking the huge, fully fenced backyard. This area is perfect for pets, playsets, and even a home ready for your chickens, bringing a touch of rural living to the suburbs. The finished basement so versatile with a full bath and two bedrooms, making it great for roommates or the must-have home office. With a 2-car garage plus an additional carport for your RV or boat, this property has plenty of room for all your vehicles and outdoor toys. Worry-free maintenance with new windows, roof, appliances, and just about anything you need for peace of mind. Enjoy quiet living while still being close to everything, only a few minutes from shopping, top-notch schools, and the beautiful Lake Allatoona. Don’t miss the 3D tour and 360° views of the gorgeous lot!
